[grade_engine/resolver.py](/mnt/c/Users/hayes/Desktop/Lets%20Have%20Some%20Fun/CNC_Tool_Engine-main/grade_engine/resolver.py)  
[grade_engine/router.py](/mnt/c/Users/hayes/Desktop/Lets%20Have%20Some%20Fun/CNC_Tool_Engine-main/grade_engine/router.py)  
